<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19396940_1381793561888616_5420463928215347047_n.jpg?oh=620556322a1d09f1e4ed1f3d2d6be951&amp;oe=59D45950\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F19396940_1381793561888616_5420463928215347047_n.jpg%3Foh%3D620556322a1d09f1e4ed1f3d2d6be951%26oe%3D59D45950&h=b3e38622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好。我係「戰月勇者」嘅小編。<br />\n因為遊戲早前同LIHKG合作，我好高興可以認識到LIHKG嘅六道仙人。我哋重好榮幸可以邀請到他出席我們聽日嘅遊戲直播。小編重知道佢原來係第一次喺遊戲直播入面出現，大家可以有機會一睹六道仙人的風采啦。<br />\n<br />\n除咗六道仙人，重有知名嘅實況主ROSE MA！<br />\n<br />\n佢哋除咗會同大家一齊玩遊戲外，重會派發禮物GA～<br />\n<br />\n大家記得聽日（<span style=\"color: red;\">6月21日</span>）晚上9時至10時去到「戰月勇者」嘅FACEBOOK專頁同佢哋一齊玩遊戲呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/heroesflick\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fheroesflick&d=ISdeuin%2BCt4GA%2BY9SdWPfgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0acd27cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/heroesflick</a></blockquote><br />\n聽日係22號呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n據我對尼個小編的理解<br />\n佢周不時打錯日期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(利申我有玩開隻驚)</blockquote><br />\n尼你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae273a3babb98db1e582237242eefcaf52b1d44","tid":292474,"uid":29335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解冇我份? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今次又賺幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人哋咪出咗聲明無賺錢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請善用回帶功能"},{"pid":"ba1b36afd18adf8154bafae5035e966083e6191f","tid":292474,"uid":43587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"